originalText: What was that? Did you hit me?
Nope! Didn't feel that at all.
You're kind of a wimp aren't you?
AAARGH! I can't feel my tail anymore!
Argh! That's gonna leave a big scar...
::Pukes blood.:: I'll... laugh about this... tomorrow...
This is not happening... this is not happening...
::Gasps for air.:: You knocked... my... air... out...
Ugh... I think that broke something...
I hope that didn't hit any of the important bits...
I can't... move... I... I... Hnnnn...
I feel... the... cold... in... my... bones...
It's time! The world has ended!
My brain juices are being squeezed out!
No... My legs don't work right...
Ouch, the ground is getting sharp!
AAAAAARRGH! I think I can see the bone!
No! Ow... The ground is biting!
I knew this day would come...
Ha! Death will only make me stronger!
Stop, drop, roll... STOP, DROP, ROLL!
It burns! Make it stop! Arrrgh!
Put it out! Put it out!
It feels so different on this side!
I can see it now - the world will burn!
I'll kill you, and you, and you...
Oooh! I don't feel so good...
Spare my life, the universe needs me.
How many ribs are you supposed to have?
Ouch... It hurts like pain. ::Grabs chest.::
Get out of my head! It's not safe there.
Oh, you won't have me. You! Won't! Have! Meeeee-heheh!
Uh-oh, I'm leaking that stuff again...
Someone get me a bucket. I'm leaking.
Are you... a figment of my imagination?
Oh no, I dreamt of this. We both die in the end...
Don't worry, it'll all be over soon...
I'll tell them you fought bravely.
::Sings:: Die, die! Die, die, die, die, die... DIE!
I hope you have something good on you.
Where do you think you're going?
Come on, you're not gonna sleep now, are you?
You got no-no stuff in your blood? Yay!
You got red coming out of you.
Red is my favorite color... No, wait, it's yellow!
Can't you do better than that?
I feel, ooooooooooh - so much better!
Oh, yes... I'm back in action!
Ahh... blue is the tastiest of colors.
I'll beat you to a nice red pulp. Nice...
This is just like whack-a-psi bug!
It tells me to break your skull.
I'll carve you up like a mushroom cake!
Say hello to my little friend!
This bullet's got your name on it!
Say hello to my little friends!
You'll be gone in a puff of smoke! ::Laughs.::
Wanna see a glowing carpet of no-walkie!?
See if you can catch this!
This is like darts, but with more death.
I'll put you on a wall, te-he!
My mind can kick your mind's ass!
I'll make your neurons pop, te-he!
I'll turn your brain to mushy-mush!
I'm gonna mind-slap you from here to Overrail!
Now you don't see me, he-he-he.
Do you like your bones iced or frozen?
Helloooooooo? Can you hear me in there?
You are gonna be so cool, te-he.
How about I burn that smile off your face!?
You could use some more fire.
There's people here. I don't know if they're real, but send help.
I need some help over here! It's $(#him/her)!
Probably just rats, but let's check anyway.
My hands can twist the universe!
I'm gonna chop you into tiny pieces!
Your head is gonna roll! Rooool!
One, two - no limbs for you!
It feels like punching someone from a distance.
